        "subject": "LU-19657 build: allow customizable release ID",
        "message": "LU-19657 build: allow customizable release ID\n\nSummary of Changes:\n\n  1. config/lustre-core.m4: Added release ID configuration option\n    - New --with-release-id configure flag (default: 1)\n    - Sets RELEASE_ID variable for build system\n  2. lustre.spec.in: Modified RPM release numbering\n    - Added release_id macro defaulting to @RELEASE_ID@\n    - Changed Release field from hardcoded \"1\" to use %{release_id}\n  3. config/lustre-build.4: Minor fix quotation\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nChange-Id: I9f7adfe69714eb9ab759ccbb593a175b7f4f2fea\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <mdiep@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62869\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Gaurang Tapase <gtapase@ddn.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\n"
